Car Hunter is a buyer intelligence tool. It does NOT provide financial,
investment, or purchase advice. Regression-based value scores, depreciation
estimates, and "deal" classifications are statistical approximations based
on the data supplied and may not reflect true market value, vehicle
condition, accident history, or mechanical soundness. Always verify
listings independently, inspect vehicles in person, and consult qualified
professionals before making a purchase decision.

Listing data is fetched from third-party websites (AutoTrader, Cazoo,
Cinch, CarWow, manufacturer programmes, and dealer groups). The author(s)
make no guarantee about the accuracy, completeness, or freshness of that
data, and are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any of
those platforms. Users are responsible for complying with each site's
terms of service when running searches.

Use at your own risk and discretion.

